== Key Insights for University Students

=== Is Boutique ECM Right For You?

*You'll likely enjoy this career if you:*
- Are energized by fast-paced, deadline-driven work on live transactions
- Love financial analysis, valuation, and capital markets
- Enjoy working with senior executives and boards on strategic decisions
- Thrive under pressure and can manage multiple competing priorities
- Value the prestige and intellectual challenge of advisory work
- Are detail-oriented but also strategic and commercial
- Want direct impact on major corporate transactions
- Are willing to work long hours for high-caliber learning and career progression

