- Prefer routine and predictable work schedules
- Are not comfortable with intense deadline pressure and long hours
- Dislike detailed document review and proof-reading
- Prefer technical analysis over client service orientation
- Want immediate work-life balance (hours improve at senior levels but challenging early career)
- Are uncomfortable with ambiguity and changing deal dynamics

